Working with VPC- NACL and Security groups

Create a VPC - select VPC and more 2 subnets and 2 availability zones

Create EC2 instance – on Ubuntu machine Edit network settings – attach the VPC that was created above

Select a public subnet and enable Auto –assign public IP
Launch instance
Connect ec2 instance on Mobaxterm

Update all packages – sudo apt update

Install python application – python3 –m http.server 8000

Edit inbound security rules under ec2 instance – to allow port 8000 image

Edit inbound rules in NACL- lower rule number gets higher priority image

http://public_ip_of_ec2:8000 – redirected to the page in the below screenshot. This is a simple python3 application. image
